{"word":"G3547 - νομοδιδάσκαλος - nomodidáskalos - nom-od-id-as'-kal-os - Doctor of the law","slug":"G3547","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">νομοδιδάσκαλος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>nomodidáskalos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>nom-od-id-as'-kal-os"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Doctor of the law"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BD;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03BF;&#x03B4;&#x03B9;&#x03B4;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03C3;&#x03BA;&#x03B1;&#x03BB;&#x03BF;&#x03C2; - nomodidaskalos</b> - <i>nom-od-id-as'-kal-os</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G3551\">G3551</a> and <a href=\"#/G1320\">G1320</a>; an <i>expounder of</i> the (Jewish) <i>law</i>, that is, a <i>Rabbi:</i> - doctor (teacher) of the law."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1772\">G1772</a>, <a href=\"#/G3544\">G3544</a>, <a href=\"#/G3545\">G3545</a>, <a href=\"#/G3548\">G3548</a>, <a href=\"#/G3549\">G3549</a>, <a href=\"#/G3550\">G3550</a>, <a href=\"#/G3551\">G3551</a>, <a href=\"#/G3891\">G3891</a>, <a href=\"#/G3892\">G3892</a>, <a href=\"#/G458\">G458</a>, <a href=\"#/G459\">G459</a>, <a href=\"#/G460\">G460</a>"}]}